{"tid":285713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前新華社副社長：佔中、港獨背後均是因為香港長期受英國殖民統治","createTime":"2017-06-16T05:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T09:03:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d4a1a2c9c89451d260ff496377f2af039c5197f","tid":285713,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170616/large/1497588246_ce7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170616%2Flarge%2F1497588246_ce7e.jpg&h=d9df20c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前新華社香港分社副社長張浚生，接受中新社訪問評論香港回歸廿年，寄語本港年青人，要加強「融入祖國的發展」就前景無限。他表示，雖然兩年多前發生佔領中環，但不能由此唱衰香港青年，認為只要對他們「加強引導融入祖國的發展，優勢明顯，前景遠大。」<br />\n<br />\n張浚生在訪問中形容，香港回歸20年以來，「愛國愛港依然是香港的主旋律」，又評價香港一國兩制「獲得了巨大成功」，但承認也有需要完善之處，包括正確引導年輕人。他指近年出現的佔中、港獨運動，背後均是因為香港長期受英國殖民統治令港人疏離自己的國家，「有錯誤的認識，就會有錯誤的行動」，又指有外部勢力策動，但他與特首梁振英一樣，都沒有提出具體證據。<br />\n<br />\n他認為不能因為有些年輕人「走了彎路就放棄，就唱衰」，應教育引導他們，創造更多機會讓香港青年融入中國發展，又稱自己年輕時候也很調皮，「老是和老師對着幹。」<br />\n<br />\n張浚生稱這幾年多次和香港青年交流，發現很多人為中國發展而欣喜，也對香港未來迷茫，但他認為香港優勢仍在，香港是全球最自由的經濟體，法律制度比較完善，作為國際金融、貿易、航運中心的地位價值獨特，長期的國際交往暢通，香港居民的總體素質也比較高，大多數香港學生外語水平就高於內地學生。他又指一帶一路、粵港澳大灣區是香港，特別是香港青年的巨大機遇。<br />\n<br />\n張浚生在訪問中又狂讚中國盛世，指現時連英國都和中國合作建設核電站，更用上中國的核電技術，而中國高鐵也成為中國製造走向世界的品牌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56835536&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56835536%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170616&d=kludMJKWjPXCT3dr1%2FxEz54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9cb6c53f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56835536%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170616&h=0b5b60f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56835536&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170616</a>"},{"pid":"275680568b1ac1bb507e499a4a92ccfe92d2e51d","tid":285713,"uid":13115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"8171934aab8f91db879da493ce037c6b1f05a6d5","tid":285713,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"基本上 1989年 後<br />\n中共黨內連少少 所謂自由派 都不存在<br />\n(胡趙連5家屯果堆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4886e246ad540c33d256518d447062e31d958c58","tid":285713,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上 1989年 後<br />\n中共黨內連少少 所謂自由派 都不存在<br />\n(胡趙許家屯果堆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ebace4f68ca104485f8556297789a8617ac205e4","tid":285713,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賤種DNA"},{"pid":"6f4bf61b80b378c5648ca7544762c5a079b1b2c9","tid":285713,"uid":2071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:47:24.000Z","msg":"相由心生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d2fd28cdb94a4b1f365f276782dbbf839fb2e0","tid":285713,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相由心生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正想講   佢地成班人都係咁既樣"},{"pid":"873c7d214a7fd0d96b17d91b46de33aead223193","tid":285713,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,